%N A039097 Numbers whose base-9 representation has the same number of 3's and 4's.
%H A039097 Chris R. Rehmann, <a href="/A039097/b039097.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%t A039097 Select[Range[0, 24100], DigitCount[#, 9, 3]==DigitCount[#, 9, 4]&] (* _Chris R. Rehmann_, Mar 17 2026 *)
%o A039097 (MATLAB) x = 0:24100; d = dec2base(x,9)-'0'; a = x(sum(d==3,2)==sum(d==4,2)); disp(regexprep(num2str(a), ' +', ', ')) % _Chris R. Rehmann_, Mar 17 2026
